WITH pgrst_source AS (INSERT INTO "public"."documents"("content", "embedding", "metadata") SELECT "pgrst_body"."content", "pgrst_body"."embedding", "pgrst_body"."metadata" FROM (SELECT $1 AS json_data) pgrst_payload, LATERAL (SELECT "content", "embedding", "metadata" FROM json_to_record(pgrst_payload.json_data) AS _("content" text, "embedding" public.vector(1536), "metadata" jsonb) ) pgrst_body  RETURNING $2) SELECT $3 AS total_result_set, pg_catalog.count(_postgrest_t) AS page_total, array[]::text[] AS header, $4::text AS body, nullif(current_setting($5, $6), $7) AS response_headers, nullif(current_setting($8, $9), $10) AS response_status, $11 AS response_inserted FROM (SELECT * FROM pgrst_source) _postgrest_t
